cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques applied to surgical videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning architectures, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also mentions the need for more data to improve the results, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with surgical videos, which could also fall under cs.RO (Robotics).
